quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  48,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  48,1,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum ko khuli fatah ataa kar di"
  48,2,taakay Allah tumhari agli pichli har kotahi se dar guzar farmaiye aur tum par apni Nemat ki takmeel kar day aur tumhe seedha rasta dukhaay
  48,3,aur tum ko zabardast nusrat bakhshay
  48,4,wohi hai jis ne mominoun ke dilon mein سکینت nazil farmai taakay apne imaan ke sath woh aik imaan aur barha len zameen aur asmano ke sab lashkar Allah ke qabza qudrat mein hain aur woh Aleem o hakeem hai
  48,5,( uss ne yeh kaam iss liye kya hai ) taakay momin mardon aur aurton ko hamesha rehne ke liye aisijannaton mein daakhil farmaiye jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi aur unn ki buraiyan unn se daur kar day Allah ke nazdeek yeh barri kamyabi hai
  48,6,"aur unn munafiq mardon aur aurton aur mushriq mardon aur aurton ko saza day jo Allah ke mutaliq buray gumaan rakhtay hain buraiee ke phair mein woh khud hi aa gay, Allah ka ghazab un par howa aur is ne un par laanat ki aur un ke liye jahannum muhayya kar di jo bohat hi bura thikana hai"
  48,7,zameen aur asmano ke lashkar Allah hi ke qabza qudrat mein hain aur woh zabardast aur hakeem hai
  48,8,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum ko shahadat dainay wala, basharat dainay wala aur khabardaar kar dainay wala bana kar bheja hai"
  48,9,"taakay ae logo, tum Allah aur is ke rasool par imaan lao aur uss ka sath do, is ki tazeem o touqeer karo aur subah o shaam is ki tasbeeh karte raho"
  48,10,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo log tum se baet kar rahay thay woh darasal Allah se baet kar rahay thay un ke haath par Allah ka haath tha ab jo is ehad ko torrey ga uss ki ehad shikni ka wabaal is ki apni hi zaat par hoga, aur jo uss ehad ko wafa kere ga jo is ne Allah se kya hai, Allah anqareeb is ko bara ajar ataa farmaiye ga"
  48,11,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, badwi arbo mein se jo log peechay chore diye gay thay ab woh aa kar zaroor tum se kahin ge ke"" hamein apne amwal aur baal bachon ki fikar ne mashgool kar rakha tha, aap hamaray liye mughfirat ki dua farmaen"" yeh log apni zabanon se woh baatein kehte hain jo un ke dilon mein nahi hoten un se kehna"" acha, yahi baat hai to kon tumahray maamla mein Allah ke faislay ko rok dainay ka kuch bhi ikhtiyar rakhta hai agar woh tumhe koi nuqsaan pahunchana chahay ya naffa bakhshna chahay? tumahray aamaal se to Allah hi bakhabar hai"
  48,12,"( magar asal baat woh nahi hai jo tum keh rahay ho ) balkay tum ne yun samgha ke rasool aur momnin apne ghar walon mein hargiz palat kar nah aa saken ge aur yeh khayaal tumahray dilon ko bohat bhala laga aur tum ne bohat buray gumaan kiye aur tum sakht bad batin log ho """
  48,13,Allah aur is ke rasool par jo log imaan nah rakhtay hon aisay kafiroon ke liye hum ne bharakti hui aag muhayya kar rakhi hai
  48,14,"asmano aur zameen ki badshahi ka maalik Allah hi hai jisay chahay maaf kere aur jisay chahay saza day, aur woh ghafoor o Raheem hai"
  48,15,"jab tum maal ghanemat haasil karne ke liye jaane lagu ge to yeh peechay chhorey jaane walay log tum se zaroor kahin ge ke hamein bhi apne sath chalne do yeh chahtay hain ke Allah ke farmaan ko badal den inn se saaf keh dena ke"" tum hargiz hamaray sath nahi chal satke, Allah pehlay hi yeh farma chuka hai"" yeh kahin ge ke"" nahi, balkay tum log hum se hasad kar rahay ho"" ( halaank baat hasad ki nahi hai ) balkay yeh log sahih baat ko kam hi samajte hain"
  48,16,"inn peechay chhorey jaane walay badwi arbo se kehna ke"" anqareeb tumhe aisay logon se larnay ke liye bulaya jaye ga jo barray zor aawar hain tum ko un se jung karni hogi ya woh Mutee ho jayen ge uss waqt agar tum ne hukum jehaad ki itaat ki to Allah tumhe acha ajar day ga, aur agar tum phir usi terhan mun mourr gay jis terhan pehlay mourr chuke ho to Allah tum ko dard naak saza day ga"
  48,17,"agar andha aur langra aur mareez jehaad ke liye nah aeye to koi harj nahi jo koi Allah aur is ke rasool ki itaat kere ga Allah usay unnjannaton mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin beh rahi hon gi, aur jo mun phairay ga usay woh dard naak azaab day ga """
  48,18,"Allah mominoun se khush ho gaya jab woh darakht ke neechay tum se baet kar rahay thay un ke dilon ka haal uss ko maloom tha, is liye is ne un par sakinat nazil farmai, un ko inaam mein qareebi fatah bakhsh"
  48,19,aur bohat sa maal ghanemat inhen ataa kar diya jisay woh ( anqareeb ) haasil karen ge Allah zabardast aur hakeem hai
  48,20,"Allah tum se bakasrat amwal ghanemat ka wada karta hai jinhein tum haasil karo ge fori tor par to yeh fatah is ne tumhe ataa kar di aur logon ke haath tumahray khilaaf uthnay se rok diye, taakay yeh mominoun ke liye aik nishani ban jaye aur Allah seedhay rastay ki taraf tumhe hadaayat bakhshay"
  48,21,"iss ke ilawa dosray aur غنیمتوں ka bhi woh tum se wada karta hai jin par tum abhi taq Qadir nahi hue ho aur Allah ne un ko ghair rakha hai, Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
  48,22,yeh kafir log agar iss waqt tum se lar gay hotay to yaqeenan peeth phair jatay aur koi haami o madadgaar nah paate
  48,23,yeh Allah ki sunnat hai jo pehlay se chali aa rahi hai aur tum Allah ki sunnat mein koi tabdeeli nah pao ge
  48,24,"wohi hai jis ne mecca ki waadi mein unn ke haath tum se aur tumahray haath unn se rok diye, halaank woh unn par tumhe ghalba ataa kar chuka tha aur jo kuch tum kar rahay thay Allah usay dekh raha tha"
  48,25,"wohi log to hain jinhon ne kufar kya aur tum ko masjid haraam se roka aur Huda ke avnton ko unn ki qurbani ki jagah nah pounchanay diya agar ( mecca mein ) aisay momin mard o aurat mojood nah hotay jinhein tum nahi jantay, aur yeh khatrah nah hota ke nadanstgi mein tum inhen pamaal kar do ge aur is se tum par harf aeye ga ( to jung nah roki jati roki woh is liye gayi ) taakay Allah apni rehmat mein jis ko chahay daakhil kar le woh momin allag ho gay hotay to ( ahal mecca mein se ) jo kafir thay un ko hum zaroor sakht saza dete"
  48,26,( yahi wajah hai ke ) jab un kafiroon ne apne dilon mein jahilana Hamiyat bitha li to Allah ne apne rasool aur mominoun par سکینت nazil farmai aur mominoun ko taqwa ki baat ka paband rakha ke wohi uss ke ziyada haq daar aur uss ke ahal thay Allah har cheez ka ilm rakhta hai
  48,27,"fi al waqea Allah ne apne rasool ko sacha khawab dikha ya tha jo theek theek haq ke mutabiq tha Insha Allah tum zaroor masjid haraam mein poooray aman ke sath daakhil ho ge, apne sir منڈواؤ ge aur baal ترشواؤ ge, aur tumhe koi khauf nah ho ga woh uss baat ko jaanta tha jisay tum nah jantay thay is liye woh khawab poora honay se pehlay uss ne yeh qareebi fatah tum ko ataa farma di"
  48,28,woh Allah hi hai jis ne apne rasool ko hadaayat aur deen haq ke sath bheja hai taakay uss ko poori jins deen par ghalib kar day aur iss haqeeqat par Allah ki gawahi kaafi hai
  48,29,"Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi WasallamAllah ke rasool hain, aur jo log un ke sath hain woh kufar par sakht aur aapas mein Raheem hain tum jab dekho ge unhen ruku o sajood, aur Allah ke fazl aur is ki khushnodi ki talab mein mashgool pao ge sajood ke asraat un ke cheharon par mojood hain jin se woh allag pehchane jatay hain yeh hai un ki sift Touraat mein aur injeel mein unn ki misaal yun di gayi hai ke goya aik khaiti hai jis ne pehlay konpal nikaali, phir is ko taqwiyat di, phir woh gudrai, phir apne tanay par khari ho gayi kaasht karne walon ko woh khush karti hai taakay kufar un ke phalnay phoolnay par jalein iss giroh ke log jo imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain Allah ne un se mughfirat aur barray ajar ka wada farmaya hai"
